        <li><a href="/disclosure-barring-service-check">who can ask for a DBS check</a></li>
      </ul>

      <p>You can also read the latest <a href="/government/news/coming-soon-disclosure-and-barring-service-to-launch-the-update-service">news about the Update Service</a>.</p>

